&lt;p&gt;Post: Chef&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: 25 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible to: Head Chef/Catering Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a chef vacancy to work within in our busy hospital kitchen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidates should have achieved their Food Preparation and cooking NVQ level 2 or the equivalent, have good communication skills and be able to work under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The candidates should hold their Food foundation certificate/Basic food hygiene and have knowledge of working within a large industrial kitchen&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Within your role you will be required to contribute on going to your own personal development with support from the departmental management team.&lt;/p&gt;
